WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:01.966
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.966 --> 00:00:03.320
Praise the Lord.

00:00:03.320 --> 00:00:05.070
Day 57.

00:00:05.070 --> 00:00:11.146
Well, I guess I stirred the internet up a little bit with the XRP video.

00:00:11.993 --> 00:00:14.236
My heart is just to help.

00:00:14.788 --> 00:00:16.969
We hear in part, we see in part.

00:00:18.462 --> 00:00:26.364
That is all I can say—whenever the Lord showed me the things he has shown me, clear back in 2017, and I’ve been praying over silver and gold.

00:00:26.364 --> 00:00:37.146
I’ve told you this stuff for a long time, and all I know is I feel an urgency in my spirit to warn the body of Christ about what’s coming.

00:00:37.679 --> 00:00:51.950
It could be a year from now, it could be six months, it could be in January, but I told you about the dream I had about the copper pot, and I’m going to go over that again today.

00:00:51.950 --> 00:01:01.879
I think it’s important for you to know about the copper pot, so I hope this video blesses you.

00:01:02.519 --> 00:01:05.489
It was like a normal night; I just went to sleep.

00:01:05.671 --> 00:01:30.432
It was just a dream, but in this dream, I was standing in a crowd of elderly men and women.

00:01:30.432 --> 00:01:38.546
They had gray beards and gray hair.

00:01:38.546 --> 00:01:46.491
They were elderly—I’m talking Moses-like beards, real long beards.

00:02:00.787 --> 00:02:23.829
I don’t know what symbolism means in dreams; I’m not a dream interpreter, so I just go by what the Holy Spirit shows me and I pray over them.

00:02:23.829 --> 00:02:44.160
In this dream, there was a circle of people surrounding a person in the middle.

00:02:44.160 --> 00:03:04.040
The person in the middle was a man whose face was shaded out, like it was blurry, so I could not see his face.

00:03:04.040 --> 00:03:30.330
But this person was completely gold, beautiful translucent gold, and he was speaking to the elders around this circle.

00:03:35.220 --> 00:03:51.680
I heard these men and women say, 'This will make us billions for the end-time harvest.

00:04:06.389 --> 00:04:06.814
This is a genius, amazing idea.

00:04:16.752 --> 00:04:17.247
This is brilliant.

00:04:17.247 --> 00:04:47.980
' I was a younger kid outside the circle and I started jumping up and down because, as the man was speaking, I could not hear him clearly.

00:04:51.148 --> 00:04:58.040
I was screaming as loud as I could, 'Please tell me!

00:05:00.575 --> 00:05:10.951
I want to know what y'all are talking about!

00:05:10.951 --> 00:05:32.580
' I started trying to reach up on those men's shoulders and pull myself up to be able to hear.

00:05:32.580 --> 00:06:00.840
The man with no face, who was completely translucent—this beautiful gold and shining with glory—leaned over and said, 'I have not forgotten you; I will tell you too.

00:06:00.840 --> 00:06:12.396
' And he spoke the name of a company to me, a crypto.

00:06:13.222 --> 00:06:22.258
He spoke this crypto name to me, a company name.

00:06:25.664 --> 00:06:33.648
I was so excited to go and tell my friends and family whoever I could about this name.

00:06:37.872 --> 00:06:54.083
I ran as fast as I could and I grew up a little bit.

00:07:01.385 --> 00:07:09.400
I was no longer a little child; I became more mature in the dream.

00:07:25.088 --> 00:07:25.372
I went, and all of a sudden, an angel appeared before me.

00:07:25.372 --> 00:07:56.000
This angel had the most beautiful blue sapphire eyes I’ve ever seen, with snow-white skin and beautiful blond-looking hair with fig leaves and stuff in his hair.

00:07:56.000 --> 00:08:13.423
He had a white robe on with golden lace and tassels on this garment.

00:08:19.211 --> 00:08:19.560
The angel followed me around.

00:08:19.560 --> 00:08:37.612
I believe it was my angel, but I’m not sure who it was, actually.

00:08:37.612 --> 00:09:08.360
I walked up to this house and I could see the beautiful bricks; it was a two-story home with a courtyard.

00:09:08.360 --> 00:09:12.053
It was gorgeous.

00:09:23.853 --> 00:09:39.160
In my front yard, I had an Aston Martin sports car, a beautiful deep blue convertible with nice silver wheels.

00:09:39.160 --> 00:09:45.954
There was snow falling outside.

00:10:03.744 --> 00:10:04.176
I was yelling to people, but they could not hear me.

00:10:04.608 --> 00:10:24.695
I was telling people before I went to the car, but they weren't hearing me.

00:10:26.240 --> 00:10:34.320
I was like, 'Hello, hello!

00:10:34.320 --> 00:10:42.345
Do you hear what I’m saying?

00:10:42.345 --> 00:10:48.560
I’m trying to tell you a name!

00:10:48.560 --> 00:10:58.890
I’m trying to tell you what’s coming!

00:10:58.890 --> 00:11:10.680
' But they could not hear what I was saying.

00:11:17.880 --> 00:11:18.270
It was like I was transparent.

00:11:19.440 --> 00:11:33.085
The angel told me, 'Hush now,' and put his fingers on my lips.

00:11:33.085 --> 00:11:44.661
He said, 'Hush now.

00:11:44.661 --> 00:11:53.428
They are not dead to self.

00:11:53.428 --> 00:12:13.880
They cannot hear what you're trying to tell them; they don't have ears to hear.

00:12:13.880 --> 00:12:26.200
' I said, 'But I’ve got to warn them!

00:12:26.200 --> 00:12:31.249
I love them!

00:12:31.249 --> 00:12:38.639
I’ve got to warn them!

00:12:38.639 --> 00:12:45.839
' He goes, 'I know your heart.

00:12:45.839 --> 00:12:49.1000
Hush now.

00:12:50.905 --> 00:12:55.217
They don't hear it.

00:12:55.217 --> 00:13:23.857
' I ran out to the car and I tried to breathe on the glass with a mist because it was cold outside.

00:13:26.640 --> 00:13:48.360
It created a fog on the glass, and I tried to write the name of the thing on the glass.

00:13:49.960 --> 00:14:00.480
The angel said, 'Hush now, hush now.

00:14:00.480 --> 00:14:04.550
They can't hear it.

00:14:04.550 --> 00:14:14.293
They're not dead to self.

00:14:14.293 --> 00:14:29.840
' I was frustrated, and the angel said, 'Look at the holly berry bush.

00:14:29.840 --> 00:14:43.119
' I had these bushes all in my courtyard with berries on them.

00:14:44.999 --> 00:15:04.370
He said, 'You will know the time of when this will take place: when the berries on the bush are turning red.

00:15:04.370 --> 00:15:16.174
Notice the berries on the bush.

00:15:16.174 --> 00:15:36.680
' The berries were turning a beautiful red color and the snow was falling.

00:15:44.519 --> 00:15:56.134
I ran upstairs and I had a Christmas party going on in my home.

00:16:01.160 --> 00:16:04.568
I saw the wreaths on the walls.

00:16:04.568 --> 00:16:20.179
It was beautiful—a rock home inside, and the fireplace was going with fire burning.

00:16:25.928 --> 00:16:42.680
I had a television above the fireplace and the news was on.

00:16:57.956 --> 00:16:58.304
I was trying to tell everybody in that party, 'Hello!

00:16:58.304 --> 00:17:07.199
' but they could not see me.

00:17:07.199 --> 00:17:12.474
They were all celebrating.

00:17:12.474 --> 00:17:30.458
They had nice sweaters on and were celebrating that the Iraqi dinar had reinstated.

00:17:30.458 --> 00:17:38.740
All of them had great wealth from this reinstatement.

00:17:38.740 --> 00:17:54.909
Now, this is not financial advice; I’m just telling you a dream.

00:17:54.909 --> 00:18:09.978
They were all celebrating the reinstatement of the Iraqi dinar because it went up in value.

00:18:09.978 --> 00:18:24.063
They were standing on a beautiful, thick Persian rug, celebrating their now windfall of money.

00:18:24.063 --> 00:18:35.179
I was trying so hard to talk to them.

00:18:35.179 --> 00:18:51.034
My wife was in the kitchen, which was beautiful and white—the cabinets, the countertops, everything.

00:19:02.919 --> 00:19:06.391
In fact, it was glowing with glory inside this beautiful kitchen.

00:19:06.391 --> 00:19:23.800
She had trays in her hands trying to serve the people with beautiful white china.

00:19:23.800 --> 00:19:50.919
She came out with a tray, and at this time, I thought I would try one more time to tell the people.

00:19:51.714 --> 00:20:03.813
The angel stood by, and there was a copper pot that had ripples and dents in it.

00:20:03.813 --> 00:20:24.949
I tried to write the name of the company again on this copper pot by breathing on it to make a fog.

00:20:24.949 --> 00:20:39.884
My wife came out of the kitchen and she said, 'Look!

00:20:39.884 --> 00:20:54.810
Look at the writing on the copper pot to warn the people!

00:20:54.810 --> 00:20:57.360
' because she could see it.

00:20:57.360 --> 00:21:26.726
Whenever she said that, the TV came on and said, 'Today we had the largest crash we've ever seen of the dollar in history—like a 1929-style crash.

00:21:26.726 --> 00:21:46.667
' It was so large you could see the Dow; everything was crashing: the dollar, the stock market.

00:22:05.799 --> 00:22:06.132
This was a worldwide huge event.

00:22:10.257 --> 00:22:31.799
The lady that was doing the news broadcast was very perplexed and upset; I could see it on her face.

00:22:31.799 --> 00:23:01.340
As the Dow Jones on the ticker was just falling, all of a sudden, everybody in the room that had a windfall with the dinar lost everything.

00:23:14.200 --> 00:23:25.760
They were standing on the Persian rug and they lost everything—it’s like the rug was pulled out from underneath them.

00:23:25.760 --> 00:23:33.493
They were weeping on the rug.

00:23:33.493 --> 00:24:01.520
They didn't see what was on the copper pot before it was too late because the copper pot was stable.

00:24:01.520 --> 00:24:16.089
What was on the copper pot was a place of refuge.

00:24:16.089 --> 00:24:33.204
Everything else changed, but the copper pot was the investment that kept everybody safe.

00:24:48.462 --> 00:24:50.559
But you didn't see it or hear it until you were dead to self.

00:24:50.559 --> 00:25:18.454
It was a warning from the Lord about future things that will take place, that you will have to be in sync with him step by step, like a soldier following the voice of the Lord.

00:25:18.454 --> 00:25:38.240
You cannot be asleep and alive to self and be able to hear him for what's coming.

00:25:53.251 --> 00:25:53.714
I heard him back in 2023, but I haven't heard him since.

00:25:53.714 --> 00:26:16.975
It takes a steady beat of a drum following the voice of the Lord on a day-to-day basis.

00:26:29.500 --> 00:26:29.830
The Lord said to me, 'Brandon, I'm giving more time.

00:26:29.830 --> 00:26:44.016
What are you going to do with these next four years?

00:26:44.016 --> 00:26:54.490
What are you going to do with this harvest?

00:26:54.490 --> 00:27:22.391
' He said the prayers of my saints, because if my people who are called by my name will humble themselves and pray, then he would hear from heaven and heal our land.

00:27:22.391 --> 00:27:27.840
He's given us a window, folks.

00:27:37.746 --> 00:27:44.315
What was going to happen in 2025 has been pushed back because of the prayers of the righteous.

00:27:44.315 --> 00:27:50.173
Do we have a window for blessing?

00:27:50.173 --> 00:28:07.640
I told you we would see a great harvest of finances before we saw a great harvest of souls.

00:28:08.480 --> 00:28:29.039
The Lord said, 'I will bring upon my remnant finances to support the churches for what's about to happen.

00:28:29.039 --> 00:29:17.039
' If you are dead to self and allowing the Holy Spirit to use you on a regular basis—not punching in a time card, but truly loving and needing the Father, reading the Bible, and being real with God—you will hear him on when to invest and when not to invest.

00:29:17.039 --> 00:29:27.400
We are in a time that is going to get very dark.

00:29:27.400 --> 00:29:35.773
There are very sobering days coming.

00:29:35.773 --> 00:29:39.039
I have been very transparent trying to warn you.

00:29:39.039 --> 00:29:51.267
I've kept really positive lately, trying to stay away from 'doom and gloom,' but it's still there.

00:29:51.267 --> 00:30:09.880
The Lord said, 'Feed their flame, increase that fire, throw gasoline on it so they're stirred up.

00:30:09.880 --> 00:30:13.120
' They hear you, but they're not hearing you.

00:30:13.120 --> 00:30:28.840
Just like I’m yelling as loud as I can but you don't see it.

00:30:28.840 --> 00:30:46.599
There are great days of darkness coming, but the body of Christ is going to walk in light.

00:30:46.599 --> 00:31:03.840
The enemy still has a plan; he didn't go away just because we have a new president.

00:31:03.840 --> 00:31:15.279
We must pray for him and his children.

00:31:15.279 --> 00:31:24.227
I've seen attempts on their lives.

00:31:24.227 --> 00:31:35.333
These people are evil, so we have to pray for a covering over them.

00:31:35.333 --> 00:31:43.216
Trump loves people; he has a family.

00:31:43.952 --> 00:31:58.464
The enemy wants to distract and silence the voice of the one crying in the wilderness.

00:31:58.464 --> 00:32:06.408
How does he try to derail the agenda?

00:32:06.408 --> 00:32:24.497
If he can't get to him through prison or attempts, maybe he targets the ones closest to him.

00:32:24.497 --> 00:32:31.708
We have to think—it's like whack-a-mole.

00:32:31.708 --> 00:32:46.720
We have to hit the enemy before he sticks his head up.

00:32:46.720 --> 00:33:04.160
We’ve got to know the plan of the enemy and stop the fires before they start.

00:33:09.303 --> 00:33:19.145
We are the head and not the tail, praying from a place of victory.

00:33:19.145 --> 00:33:35.256
I’m telling you as a Watchman on the wall, a major storm is coming.

00:33:35.256 --> 00:33:39.336
A plague is coming.

00:33:39.336 --> 00:33:46.493
Can we stop it?

00:33:46.493 --> 00:34:00.360
No, because the Bible says in the last days there'll be plagues, pestilence, wars, and famines.

00:34:00.360 --> 00:34:04.474
But as for me and my house, we will serve the Lord.

00:34:04.474 --> 00:34:20.373
When the enemy comes in like a flood, the Spirit of the Lord will raise a standard.

00:34:20.373 --> 00:34:27.524
Arise, shine, for the light has come!

00:34:27.524 --> 00:34:38.542
It’s not for us to shrink back like Chicken Little.

00:34:38.542 --> 00:34:47.700
It was dark in Egypt, but it was light in Goshen.

00:34:47.700 --> 00:34:50.639
What makes us different?

00:34:59.159 --> 00:35:05.839
I told you Holy Ghost Woodstocks were going to happen all throughout the world.

00:35:21.616 --> 00:35:22.160
People operating in the gifts of the Spirit will be widespread.

00:35:35.440 --> 00:35:42.540
I saw football stadiums full of people—the Dallas Cowboys stadium, the San Francisco 49ers stadium—major arenas full of people giving God glory.

00:35:42.540 --> 00:35:47.257
They weren't big enough.

00:35:47.257 --> 00:36:06.880
Texas Motor Speedway had acres of fields with screens and revival taking place, with people in tents just trying to be there.

00:36:06.880 --> 00:36:19.920
There is a great move of God this world has never seen before.

00:36:21.095 --> 00:36:36.474
The angel armies are being sent to help us bring forth the lost.

00:36:36.474 --> 00:36:56.370
But God is going to bring forth great finances to fund this end-time harvest.

00:36:56.370 --> 00:37:10.674
If God can get it through you, he will get it to you.

00:37:10.674 --> 00:37:23.140
But if you're all about yourself—buying five Ferraris and Lamborghinis—God won't use you that way.

00:37:41.205 --> 00:37:41.440
It's not bad to have nice things, as long as those things don't have you.

00:37:41.440 --> 00:38:04.775
God has the right people in the right place to bring forth finances to spread throughout the world.

00:38:04.775 --> 00:38:29.904
It's going to take people with great influence, like Elon Musk, when the glory of the Lord shows off.

00:38:29.904 --> 00:38:40.200
First there was a fragrance, then there was fire.

00:38:40.200 --> 00:38:44.164
Worship is a weapon.

00:38:44.164 --> 00:39:08.195
I get excited about what's coming, but I also have apprehension because I know what's coming on the other side.

00:39:08.195 --> 00:39:21.540
War is going to increase; it's going to get really ugly in Europe.

00:39:21.540 --> 00:39:47.319
You're going to see war escalate in Israel like never before, with Turkey getting involved.

00:39:59.670 --> 00:40:00.005
We will see war on our own soil.

00:40:00.005 --> 00:40:13.369
But the Lord is giving us a reprieve of time to bring a harvest in.

00:40:13.369 --> 00:40:21.693
He's going to shake the nations.

00:40:38.480 --> 00:40:38.813
The finances—people were rejoicing because they had a reinstatement of the dinar.

00:40:49.900 --> 00:40:50.160
They had the windfall, but they weren't in step.

00:40:50.160 --> 00:41:11.810
They were celebrating their victory, but then they lost it because they didn't stay in step with the Father.

00:41:11.810 --> 00:41:23.182
This will require you to stay in step on a day-to-day basis.

00:41:23.182 --> 00:41:39.800
This isn't financial advice; I'm just telling you what I felt the Holy Spirit told me.

00:41:39.800 --> 00:41:51.554
I'm an imperfect vessel, so you filter it through the Spirit.

00:41:51.554 --> 00:42:02.410
We’re going to pray for you to have ears to hear.

00:42:02.410 --> 00:42:12.220
Father, I thank you for every person here.

00:42:29.639 --> 00:42:29.900
We take authority over demonic distractions.

00:42:29.900 --> 00:42:39.969
We plead the blood of Jesus over everyone.

00:42:58.210 --> 00:42:58.435
We send angels for prosperity.

00:42:58.435 --> 00:43:15.000
I thank you that we will hear your voice so clearly it’ll be like a pin drop.

00:43:15.000 --> 00:43:20.966
We’ll hear whispers from you.

00:43:41.903 --> 00:43:53.280
I believe for everyone here that you anoint them to bring forth finances, to be the man with the pitcher in his hand to pour out the blessing.

00:43:55.834 --> 00:44:06.000
We are not dams that hoard in greed; we are a river that flows.

00:44:06.000 --> 00:44:24.737
I thank you for the anointing of the Holy Spirit to prosper and be in health.

00:44:40.950 --> 00:44:41.319
We thank you that Jesus Christ is coming soon.

00:44:51.660 --> 00:44:57.810
I pray for their bodies—that they're healed from cancer, diabetes, heart disease, glaucoma, cataracts, and brain tumors.

00:45:11.143 --> 00:45:11.514
I thank you that they are healed from Alzheimer's and dementia.

00:45:11.514 --> 00:45:18.529
No depression, no seasonal affective disorder, no anxiety.

00:45:18.529 --> 00:45:34.210
We speak to torment in the name of Jesus and command it to be gone from their dreams.

00:45:34.210 --> 00:45:41.500
Night terrors, PTSD, and war trauma—we call for healing.

00:45:41.500 --> 00:45:48.399
We thank you for life more abundantly.

00:45:48.399 --> 00:46:03.062
We thank you for that word dwelling on the inside of us like a mighty rushing wind.

00:46:03.062 --> 00:46:15.526
We will be the salt of the earth to bring forth a great harvest of souls.

00:46:33.716 --> 00:46:36.128
I thank you for drawing us closer to you.

00:46:36.128 --> 00:46:38.417
Children hear their father, and we will hear you.

00:46:40.370 --> 00:46:43.524
We bind the spirit of confusion.

00:46:43.524 --> 00:46:50.013
Read Ephesians over and over again.

00:46:50.013 --> 00:47:15.700
Father, I thank you for Elon Musk—that he is radically born again and his technology is used for the glory of God.

00:47:15.700 --> 00:48:02.000
I thank you for President Trump and his family.

00:48:02.000 --> 00:48:11.920
We put a hedge of protection around his children and grandkids.

00:48:11.920 --> 00:48:19.440
No weapon formed against them shall prosper.

00:48:19.440 --> 00:48:36.607
We thank you that you will expose all darkness, including pedophilia rings.

00:48:36.607 --> 00:48:44.119
We will be shocked at who is involved.

00:48:44.119 --> 00:48:53.600
We thank you for protecting the children.

00:48:53.600 --> 00:49:01.709
I thank you for this time of acceleration.

00:49:01.709 --> 00:49:35.240
We call forth justice in Hollywood, in athletics, in politics, and in the medical arena.

00:49:37.754 --> 00:49:40.300
The pharmakia will be exposed.

00:49:49.130 --> 00:50:02.720
You are a just God, and judgment begins in the house of the Lord first.

00:50:15.383 --> 00:50:30.080
You shake the darkness and shine the light.

00:50:30.080 --> 00:50:46.880
I ask for mercy for my children and family.

00:51:08.730 --> 00:51:09.420
I thank you for your angels that keep us.

00:52:46.680 --> 00:52:47.273
I pray over Asia today.

00:52:50.240 --> 00:53:23.233
You specifically told me to pray over South Korea, and we call for revival.

00:53:23.233 --> 00:53:51.566
We’re wanting to learn which translation is best for our South Korean channel.

00:53:51.566 --> 00:54:18.115
If you live there, please help us on our community thread.

00:54:55.344 --> 00:54:58.589
Father, I thank you for Korea.

00:54:58.599 --> 00:56:03.715
Raise up men and women to be bold.

00:56:06.939 --> 00:56:17.646
We say that the blinders of false religion, like Buddhism, are broken.

00:56:17.646 --> 00:56:29.559
This devil is coming under our feet.

00:56:32.096 --> 00:56:57.660
We call for an exposing of darkness throughout Asia, India, Pakistan, and the Middle East.

00:56:57.660 --> 00:57:44.280
There is a great move of the Spirit on these nations.

00:57:44.620 --> 00:57:54.720
We will walk in demonstrations of glory, setting the captives free.

00:57:54.720 --> 00:58:09.200
I thank you for a great harvest of souls in Israel and Egypt.

00:58:17.293 --> 00:58:20.780
We thank you for the cabinet for President Trump.

00:58:21.853 --> 00:58:25.827
We pray for our pastors.

00:58:27.720 --> 00:58:33.870
We expose adultery and perversions.

00:58:33.880 --> 00:58:53.836
I saw people standing on platforms preaching while walking in sin, and they fall over dead.

00:58:53.836 --> 00:59:00.827
It’s going to be like Ananias and Sapphira soon.

00:59:01.209 --> 00:59:12.698
You better repent and get off that platform if you’re walking in that.

00:59:12.698 --> 00:59:18.400
I saw judgment starting to happen in churches.

00:59:34.035 --> 00:59:51.829
I hear this prophetically to warn you.

00:59:51.839 --> 01:00:24.730
If you’re preaching and you think you’re covered while committing adultery, you’ll fall over dead just like Ananias and Sapphira.

01:00:24.730 --> 01:00:37.820
I’m trying to warn you; I don't want you to go to hell.

01:00:37.820 --> 01:00:45.446
Judgment begins in the house of the Lord.

01:00:45.446 --> 01:01:05.376
This goes through the Baptists, Methodists, Catholics, Assemblies of God—all denominations.

01:01:20.913 --> 01:01:24.440
It will be like a house of fire, a Refiner’s Fire, purifying and burning up the chaff.

01:01:37.926 --> 01:01:39.453
A great Refiner’s Fire is coming through my churches as of today, says the Lord.

01:01:52.293 --> 01:01:52.506
You have nothing to fear if you're under the blood.

01:01:52.506 --> 01:02:09.394
But if you are practicing sin on purpose, this judgment will come.

01:02:09.394 --> 01:02:15.919
No more warnings, no more time.

01:02:15.919 --> 01:02:24.566
I will protect my beloved sheep from the wolves in sheep’s clothing.

01:02:24.566 --> 01:02:33.925
Search us, God, and create in us a clean heart.

01:02:33.925 --> 01:02:38.740
That was a heavy word.

01:02:38.740 --> 01:02:46.259
I feel the weight of it all over my home.

01:02:46.259 --> 01:02:51.120
We repent before a holy God.

01:02:51.120 --> 01:02:57.580
We thank you for the blood of Jesus.

01:02:57.580 --> 01:03:05.547
What can wash away my sin?

01:03:05.547 --> 01:03:10.783
Nothing but the blood of Jesus.

01:03:10.783 --> 01:03:17.714
We take this communion.

01:03:30.214 --> 01:03:33.207
You became sickness and disease for us; by your stripes, we are healed.

01:03:34.207 --> 01:03:42.029
We apply the blood of Jesus over our flesh.

01:03:42.029 --> 01:03:52.392
If you've messed up, you take this blood and you apply it.

01:03:52.392 --> 01:04:05.355
You confess your sins to an elder and make it right.

01:04:05.355 --> 01:04:13.411
You can't just bury it, especially in leadership.

01:04:13.411 --> 01:04:31.436
We thank you, Father, that you are faithful and just to forgive us.

01:04:36.839 --> 01:04:42.990
This isn't just for ministers; it's for your house too.

01:04:54.240 --> 01:04:56.430
You've been cheating on your wife or husband and you think it's okay?

01:04:56.430 --> 01:04:57.729
No more.

01:04:57.729 --> 01:05:03.799
You're opening the door for the devourer.

01:05:03.799 --> 01:05:09.420
Don't give the devil an inch.

01:05:09.420 --> 01:05:19.379
He is a roaring lion seeking whom he may devour.

01:05:19.379 --> 01:05:27.470
Don't open the door; keep it shut.

01:05:27.470 --> 01:05:39.199
If you have a relationship with another woman, cut it off.

01:05:39.199 --> 01:05:45.999
Expose the darkness; it's not worth your soul.

01:05:45.999 --> 01:05:49.400
It's not worth going to hell.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.050
Eternity is forever.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
I hope this video blessed you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
Thank you for your support.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
We’re starting the Korean channel to spread the gospel in Asia.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
God bless you all.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.050
Jesus loves you.
